      • createdResource

        public ResourceT createdResource(String key)
        Gets a resource created or updated by a create-update task in this group.

        This method can return null if the resource has not yet created that happens if the responsible task is not yet selected for execution or it's it progress or provided key is invalid.

        Parameters:
        key - the resource key
        Returns:
        the created resource
